Package cascom.fipa.envelope

Interface Summary
EnvelopeCodec Interface for all codecs intended for coding the message envelope of FIPA ACL message.
EnvelopeConstants fipa.mts.env.rep.bitefficient.std concrete envelope transport syntax related constants.
 

Class Summary
BitEfficientEnvelopeCodec Main class for bit-efficient encoder and decoder.
EnvelopeDecoder Implements a decoder for bit-efficient envelopes as specificied in FIPA Specification number 88 (FIPA Agent Message Transport Envelope in Bit-Efficient Encoding Specification).
EnvelopeEncoder Implements an encoder for bit-efficient envelopes as specificied in FIPA Specification number 88 (FIPA Agent Message Transport Envelope in Bit-Efficient Encoding Specification).
